## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's conversion drivers feature for funnel analysis, which identifies events and behaviors that correlate with user conversions or drop-offs between funnel steps, providing correlation scores, frequency metrics, and event property analysis for users on Growth and Enterprise plans.

